nload PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2527653\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2527653\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 17, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104fte1665702917323.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fte1665702917323.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fte1665702917323.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"fte1665702917323\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Delete or nullify a set of records.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fte1665702917323__section_yv2_wrr_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d512661e50\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fte1665702917323__p_d130745e1_d130746e1_d130747e1\">The connector is responsible for any necessary\n        locking.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"fte1665702917323__table_d15647e1_d15648e1_d15649e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Modes</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fte1665702917323__table_d15647e1_d15648e1_d15649e1__entry__1\">Mode</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fte1665702917323__table_d15647e1_d15648e1_d15649e1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fte1665702917323__table_d15647e1_d15648e1_d15649e1__entry__1\"> Mode 0 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fte1665702917323__table_d15647e1_d15648e1_d15649e1__entry__2\">Delete all records identified by the profile in the\n                ‘if’ list or where structure.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fte1665702917323__table_d15647e1_d15648e1_d15649e1__entry__1\">Mode 1</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fte1665702917323__table_d15647e1_d15648e1_d15649e1__entry__2\">Update the foreign key fields to NULL (the native\n                missing value symbol of the DBMS) for all records identified by the value of the\n                foreign key fields in the ‘if’ list.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fte1665702917323__section_os3_r3y_bcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d512661e105\">From Uniface</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Preconditions realized by Uniface—The table that <code class=\"ph codeph\">Wildcard</code> is requested for\n        is open.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"fte1665702917323__table_d15650e1_d15651e1_d15652e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Information Available from Uniface</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fte1665702917323__table_d15650e1_d15651e1_d15652e1__entry__1\">Data Structure-&gt;Element</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fte1665702917323__table_d15650e1_d15651e1_d15652e1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fte1665702917323__table_d15650e1_d15651e1_d15652e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;TMEnabled</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fte1665702917323__table_d15650e1_d15651e1_d15652e1__entry__2\">Indicates whether the connector is\n                TM-controlled.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fte1665702917323__table_d15650e1_d15651e1_d15652e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;udrv</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fte1665702917323__table_d15650e1_d15651e1_d15652e1__entry__2\">Points to the connector workspace if a workspace was\n                requested in the <code class=\"ph codeph\">Info</code> request.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fte1665702917323__table_d15650e1_d15651e1_d15652e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;udrvini</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fte1665702917323__table_d15650e1_d15651e1_d15652e1__entry__2\">Unique identification of the current logon\n                path.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fte1665702917323__table_d15650e1_d15651e1_d15652e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;ufldlst</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fte1665702917323__table_d15650e1_d15651e1_d15652e1__entry__2\">Field list that describes all the fields in the\n                table.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fte1665702917323__table_d15650e1_d15651e1_d15652e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;uiflst</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fte1665702917323__table_d15650e1_d15651e1_d15652e1__entry__2\">Identifies the record to be updated.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fte1665702917323__table_d15650e1_d15651e1_d15652e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;uwlist</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fte1665702917323__table_d15650e1_d15651e1_d15652e1__entry__2\">Identifies the records to be deleted or nullified for\n                ISAM-like DBMSs.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fte1665702917323__section_twy_r3y_bcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d512661e215\">To Uniface</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"fte1665702917323__table_d15653e1_d15654e1_d15655e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Connector Request Return Values</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fte1665702917323__table_d15653e1_d15654e1_d15655e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fte1665702917323__table_d15653e1_d15654e1_d15655e1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fte1665702917323__table_d15653e1_d15654e1_d15655e1__entry__1\">0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fte1665702917323__table_d15653e1_d15654e1_d15655e1__entry__2\">Wildcard delete/nullify was successful.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fte1665702917323__table_d15653e1_d15654e1_d15655e1__entry__1\">-3</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fte1665702917323__table_d15653e1_d15654e1_d15655e1__entry__2\">Exceptional error.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fte1665702917323__table_d15653e1_d15654e1_d15655e1__entry__1\">-9</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fte1665702917323__table_d15653e1_d15654e1_d15655e1__entry__2\">I/O server logon error.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fte1665702917323__table_d15653e1_d15654e1_d15655e1__entry__1\">-16</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fte1665702917323__table_d15653e1_d15654e1_d15655e1__entry__2\">DBMS reported network error. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fte1665702917323__p_d130757e1_d130758e1_d130759e1\">When the connector request return value is less than\n        0, an error code must be supplied in <code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;udrverr</code>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fte1665702917323__section_ktp_1sr_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d512661e291\">Service Functions</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"fte1665702917323__ul_blb_bsr_gwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fte1665702917323__li_d46889e1_d46890e1_d46891e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ktq1665702918659.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ktq1665702918659.html\" title=\"Determines if a record matches the profile specified in the uiflst structure and the uwhrlst structure.\">uhitchk</a>\n</code>—checks if a record matches the specified selection profile. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fte1665702917323__li_d46892e1_d46893e1_d46894e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vaz1665702918763.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vaz1665702918763.html\" title=\"Updates the fields appearing in the ‘if’ list to NULL in the general I/O buffer.\">unullify</a>\n</code>—sets the foreign key fields in the <code class=\"ph codeph\">iflist</code> to NULL. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fte1665702917323__li_d46895e1_d46896e1_d46897e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sxa1665702918900.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sxa1665702918900.html\" title=\"Informs the connector whether it needs to continue searching through the preferred index.\">uready</a>\n</code>—use with an ISAM-like DBMS in combination with <code class=\"ph codeph\">uhitchk</code>, to stop\n          searching through the preferred index. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fte1665702917323__section_l5q_bsr_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d512661e348\">TM-Controlled Connectors</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">TM-controlled DBMS connectors are not allowed to begin, commit, or rollback\n        transactions.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/azl1665702915888.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uctrl</a><p>Exchanges general information between Uniface and the connector, and describes a table.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xrb1665702976299.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>TM-Controlled DBMS Connectors</a><p>A database connector can be controlled by a transaction manager only if it is TM-capable. Uniface does not provide TM-controlled connectors and does not directly support third-party transaction managers. However, you can use the APIs provided by the Database Connector Interface to build a custom database connector that does.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527653\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527653\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Wildcard delete/nullify (*) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 17, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Delete or nullify a set of records. Description The connector is responsible for any necessary locking. Table 1. Modes Mode Description Mode 0 Delete all records identified by the profile in the ‘if’ list or where structure. Mode 1 Update the foreign key fields to NULL (the native missing value symbol of the DBMS) for all records identified by the value of the foreign key fields in the ‘if’ list. From Uniface Preconditions realized by Uniface—The table that Wildcard is requested for is open. Table 2. Information Available from Uniface Data Structure->Element Description uctrl->TMEnabled Indicates whether the connector is TM-controlled. uctrl->udrv Points to the connector workspace if a workspace was requested in the Info request. uctrl->udrvini Unique identification of the current logon path. uctrl->ufldlst Field list that describes all the fields in the table. uctrl->uiflst Identifies the record to be updated. uctrl->uwlist Identifies the records to be deleted or nullified for ISAM-like DBMSs. To Uniface Table 3. Connector Request Return Values Value Description 0 Wildcard delete/nullify was successful. -3 Exceptional error. -9 I/O server logon error. -16 DBMS reported network error. When the connector request return value is less than 0, an error code must be supplied in uctrl->udrverr . Service Functions uhitchk —checks if a record matches the specified selection profile. unullify —sets the foreign key fields in the iflist to NULL. uready —use with an ISAM-like DBMS in combination with uhitchk , to stop searching through the preferred index. TM-Controlled Connectors TM-controlled DBMS connectors are not allowed to begin, commit, or rollback transactions. Related Links uctrl Exchanges general information between Uniface and the connector, and describes a table. TM-Controlled DBMS Connectors A database connector can be controlled by a transaction manager only if it is TM-capable. Uniface does not provide TM-controlled connectors and does not directly support third-party transaction managers. However, you can use the APIs provided by the Database Connector Interface to build a custom database connector that does. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}